  "excerpt": "<p>Overview DataTools Pro Explorer for Snowflake is a simple data exploration tool to aggregate, filter, and sort data quickly while generating SQL code for you. DataTools Pro Explorer allows you to explore Snowflake tables and views. Our goal is to enable users of all skill levels to quickly analyze large volumes of data inside Snowflake, [&hellip;]</p>",
  "content_html": "\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_76 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Table of Contents</p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle</span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"/></svg></span></span></span></a></span></div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Overview\" >Overview</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Key_Features\" >Key Features</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Report_an_Issue_or_Enhancement\" >Report an Issue or Enhancement</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#DataTools_Pro_Explorer_for_Snowflake_Installation\" >DataTools Pro Explorer for Snowflake Installation</a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#1_From_Snowflake_Marketplace\" >1. From Snowflake Marketplace</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#2_From_Internal_Marketplace_Testing_Org_Only_and_Strategic_Partnerships\" >2. From Internal Marketplace (Testing / Org Only, and Strategic Partnerships)</a></li></ul></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Setup_Permissions\" >Setup / Permissions</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Usage_%E2%80%93_Explore_Data\" >Usage &#8211; Explore Data</a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Select_Columns\" >Select Columns</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Aggregation\" >Aggregation</a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Dimensions\" >Dimensions</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Measures_%E2%80%93_Numeric_values\" >Measures &#8211; Numeric values</a></li></ul></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Filter\" >Filter</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Sort\" >Sort</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Query_Preview\" >Query Preview</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Limit\" >Limit</a></li></ul></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Table_Output\" >Table Output</a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-18\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Export_data\" >Export data</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-19\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Search_data\" >Search data</a></li></ul></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-20\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Saving_and_Loading_Saved_Queries\" >Saving and Loading Saved Queries</a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-21\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Loading_a_Saved_Query\" >Loading a Saved Query</a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-22\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Filter_by_Categories\" >Filter by Categories</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-23\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#View_Saved_Query_Details\" >View Saved Query Details</a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-24\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Manage_Categories\" >Manage Categories</a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-25\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Choose_a_Category_to_manage\" >Choose a Category to manage</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-26\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Add_category_values_to_a_category\" >Add category values to a category</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-27\" href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer/#Delete_category_values\" >Delete category values</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Overview\"></span>Overview<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>DataTools Pro Explorer for Snowflake is a simple data exploration tool to aggregate, filter, and sort data quickly while generating SQL code for you. DataTools Pro Explorer allows you to explore Snowflake tables and views. Our goal is to enable users of all skill levels to quickly analyze large volumes of data inside Snowflake, or self-serve to export data. With an intuitive Streamlit-based interface, DataTools Pro Explorer accelerates data access and simple data exploration.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://app.snowflake.com/marketplace/listing/GZ1M6ZUJBYW/datatools-pro-datatools-pro-explorer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\"><strong>View Snowflake Marketplace Listing</strong></a> | <a href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/datatools-pro-explorer-for-snowflake-release-notes/\" title=\"DataTools Pro Explorer for Snowflake Release Notes\">Release Notes</a> | <a href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/snowflake-adoption-blueprint-speeds-up-time-to-value/\" title=\"Snowflake Adoption Blueprint Speeds up Time to Value\">Snowflake Adoption Blueprint</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Simple Alternative to Snowflake Workspaces - Data Tools Pro Explorer Nov 2025\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/su5oFm4k6p4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Key_Features\"></span>Key Features<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Visual Explorer</strong> – Aggregate, filter,r and sort your data</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Schema &amp; Table Exploration</strong> – browse databases, schemas, and tables and views to select your data set</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Instant Query Execution</strong> – Run queries directly in Snowflake using your assigned warehouse.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>No-Code Analysis</strong>– Empower non-technical users to select aggregate, explore, and export data.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Secure &amp; Native</strong> – Runs entirely inside Snowflake, no data leaves your environment (unless it is exported).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Save and Tag Explorations for Sharing</strong> &#8211; Save and share your explorations for others to view and access</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"support\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Report_an_Issue_or_Enhancement\"></span>Report an Issue or Enhancement<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Run into an issue or have an enhancement request? We are always here to help! Email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@datatoolspro.com\">support@datatoolspro.com</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"DataTools_Pro_Explorer_for_Snowflake_Installation\"></span>DataTools Pro Explorer for Snowflake Installation<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_From_Snowflake_Marketplace\"></span>1. From Snowflake Marketplace<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Navigate to <strong>Snowsight</strong> → <strong>Data Products</strong> → <strong>Marketplace</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Search for <strong>DataTools Pro Explorer</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click <strong>Get</strong> to install the application into your Snowflake account.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_From_Internal_Marketplace_Testing_Org_Only_and_Strategic_Partnerships\"></span>2. From Internal Marketplace (Testing / Org Only, and Strategic Partnerships)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If your org admin has published DataTools Pro Visual SQL Builder internally through private beta or other enterprise programs.</p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Go to <strong>Data Products</strong> → <strong>Internal Marketplace</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Locate <strong>DataTools Pro Explorer</strong> and install.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Setup_Permissions\"></span>Setup / Permissions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>After installation:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Grant the application the ability to read from the required databases/schemas.</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>GRANT USAGE ON DATABASE &lt;db_name> TO APPLICATION DATATOOLS_PRO_EXPLORER;\nGRANT USAGE ON SCHEMA &lt;db_name>.&lt;schema_name> TO APPLICATION DATATOOLS_PRO_EXPLORER;\n-- GRANT SELECT ON TABLES WITHIN YOUR SCHEMA\nGRANT SELECT ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA &lt;db_name>.&lt;schema_name> TO APPLICATION DATATOOLS_PRO_EXPLORER;\n-- GRANT SELECT ON VIEWS WITHIN YOUR SCHEMA\nGRANT SELECT ON ALL VIEWS IN SCHEMA &lt;db_name>.&lt;schema_name> TO APPLICATION  DATATOOLS_PRO_EXPLORER;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Once permissions are set, open the app from <strong>Apps → <strong>DataTools Pro Explorer</strong></strong> in Snowsight.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Usage_%E2%80%93_Explore_Data\"></span>Usage &#8211; Explore Data<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Launch the app</strong> from Snowsight → Data Products → Apps.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Explore your databases and schemas, and select 1 single table or view.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Use the <strong>DataTools Pro Explorer</strong> to create queries without writing code.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Execute queries against your warehouse and view results instantly.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Select_Columns\"></span>Select Columns<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-dominant-color=\"f2f6fa\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #f2f6fa;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"593\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-11-1024x593.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11938 not-transparent\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-11-1024x593.webp 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-11-300x174.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-11-768x445.webp 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-11-1536x890.webp 1536w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-11-2048x1187.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Aggregation\"></span>Aggregation<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dimensions\"></span>Dimensions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Select columns that act as dimensions to group your data by</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Measures_%E2%80%93_Numeric_values\"></span>Measures &#8211; Numeric values <span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>These are aggregated numeric values.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Column</strong>&#8211; The numeric field to aggregate.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Function</strong>&#8211; Aggregation function such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><code>COUNT</code> → counts rows or values.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><code>SUM</code> → total of the values.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><code>AVG</code> → mean.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><code>MIN</code> / <code>MAX</code> → smallest or largest</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Alias</strong> &#8211; The name you want for the output field (default in screenshot is <code>count_ordinal_position</code>).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-dominant-color=\"fcfcfb\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #fcfcfb;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"602\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-15-1024x602.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11942 not-transparent\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-15-1024x602.webp 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-15-300x176.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-15-768x451.webp 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-15-1536x903.webp 1536w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-15-2048x1204.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Filter\"></span>Filter<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Set one or multiple filters, where you can utilize standard Snowflake conditions. DataTools Pro Explorer supports combining multiple filters. It supports combining AND and &#8220;OR&#8221; conditions, but does not currently allow you to mix and match AND / OR conditions. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-dominant-color=\"fafafb\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #fafafb;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"339\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-12-1024x339.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11939 not-transparent\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-12-1024x339.webp 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-12-300x99.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-12-768x254.webp 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-12-1536x509.webp 1536w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-12.webp 1827w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sort\"></span>Sort<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Select multiple columns to order by. Set for each column an ASC (ascending) or DESC (descending) sort order.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-dominant-color=\"f5f7fb\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #f5f7fb;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"177\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-16-1024x177.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11943 not-transparent\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-16-1024x177.webp 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-16-300x52.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-16-768x133.webp 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-16-1536x265.webp 1536w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-16-2048x354.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Query_Preview\"></span>Query Preview<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>DataTools Pro Explorer generates a live SQL preview based on the combination of options you select. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click &#8220;Run query&#8221; to run the SQL query and view results.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-dominant-color=\"f7f9f9\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #f7f9f9;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-17-1024x200.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11944 not-transparent\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-17-1024x200.webp 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-17-300x58.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-17-768x150.webp 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-17-1536x299.webp 1536w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-17-2048x399.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Limit\"></span>Limit<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Limit the number of rows you return.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Table_Output\"></span>Table Output<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Export_data\"></span>Export data<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Export your data to CSV by clicking on the download icon</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Search_data\"></span>Search data<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Search for individual data points within your table.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-dominant-color=\"f5faf5\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #f5faf5;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"126\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-18-1024x126.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11945 not-transparent\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-18-1024x126.webp 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-18-300x37.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-18-768x94.webp 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-18-1536x188.webp 1536w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-18-2048x251.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"support\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Saving_and_Loading_Saved_Queries\"></span>Saving and Loading Saved Queries<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To save an exploration for future access, simply click &#8220;Save&#8221; query. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img data-dominant-color=\"f2f6f5\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-20.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12063 not-transparent\" style=\"--dominant-color: #f2f6f5; width:496px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-20.webp 940w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-20-300x115.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-20-768x294.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p> Upon clicking &#8220;Save Query&#8221; you can name and tag the query with a category.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-dominant-color=\"ecf1f9\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #ecf1f9;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"279\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-21-1024x279.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12064 not-transparent\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-21-1024x279.webp 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-21-300x82.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-21-768x209.webp 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-21-1536x418.webp 1536w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-21.webp 1814w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Loading_a_Saved_Query\"></span>Loading a Saved Query<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To access and load previously saved queries, click on the &#8220;Saved Queries&#8221; item in the left hand manu</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img data-dominant-color=\"eeedee\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"490\" height=\"212\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-22.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12065 not-transparent\" style=\"--dominant-color: #eeedee; width:371px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-22.webp 490w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-22-300x130.webp 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Filter_by_Categories\"></span>Filter by Categories<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>To narrow the scope and list of queries, you can select categories that were set while saving or editing a query.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-dominant-color=\"f7faf8\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #f7faf8;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"223\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-24-1024x223.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12067 not-transparent\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-24-1024x223.webp 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-24-300x65.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-24-768x167.webp 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-24-1536x334.webp 1536w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-24.webp 1664w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"View_Saved_Query_Details\"></span>View Saved Query Details<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking on a saved query will expand an accordian with details about the query:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Database</strong>: Database used by explorer</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Schema</strong>: Schema used by explorer</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Table</strong>: Snowflake table accessed by explorer</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Categories (Tags)</strong>: Categorization for simplified serch and access</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>SQL Query: </strong>The SQL query generated by explorer</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-dominant-color=\"f9fbfc\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #f9fbfc;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"368\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-26-1024x368.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12069 not-transparent\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-26-1024x368.webp 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-26-300x108.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-26-768x276.webp 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-26-1536x552.webp 1536w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-26-2048x736.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Run:</strong> Run the SQL Query</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Edit with Explorer: </strong>Edit your existing query in explorer</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Rename: </strong>Rename your query</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Edit Tags: </strong>Add and remove tags</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Delete: </strong>Delete your query</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"support\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Manage_Categories\"></span>Manage Categories<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Manage your categories, so they can be applied to your existing queries.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Choose_a_Category_to_manage\"></span>Choose a Category to manage<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Select &#8220;Manage Categories&#8221; dropdown</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Line of Business</strong>&#8211; Line of business like marketing or sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Topics</strong>&#8211; Open ended topics can be treated as tags that are relevant to your business.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-dominant-color=\"f3f3f4\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #f3f3f4;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"402\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-27-1024x402.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12070 not-transparent\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-27-1024x402.webp 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-27-300x118.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-27-768x302.webp 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-27.webp 1248w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Add_category_values_to_a_category\"></span>Add category values to a category<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In the &#8220;Add New Value&#8221; section, enter a value name</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click Add value</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img data-dominant-color=\"dde7f6\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"882\" height=\"336\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-28.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12071 not-transparent\" style=\"--dominant-color: #dde7f6; width:512px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-28.webp 882w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-28-300x114.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-28-768x293.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 882px) 100vw, 882px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Delete_category_values\"></span>Delete category values <span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Select 1 or multiple categories</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click &#8220;Delete Selected&#8221; to remove the category value(s)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img data-dominant-color=\"f6f7f8\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"902\" height=\"396\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-29.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12072 not-transparent\" style=\"--dominant-color: #f6f7f8; width:490px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-29.webp 902w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-29-300x132.webp 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/image-29-768x337.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 902px) 100vw, 902px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"support\"></h2>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n"
}